author: rcm
msg: Combined Viewer and ViewerAssistant into one class, allowing a simpler setup, and use of the viewing mechanism.  Viewer is now go-between between the underlying Java UI (Awt) and the viewing mechanism.

author: rcm
msg: Datahelper now passes on the changes to object to the dirty object set, allowing the viewer to refresh views that have changed.

author: rcm
msg: Moved the adding of the object to the dirty set until after the iteration through the fields of the object in the DataHelper.
